title: CycoreFX Plugins for After Effects
description:
Great to have if you have installed After Effects CS3 and did not get the CC- Plugins. 


CycoreFX HD 1.6 includes 7 new plug-ins, extending the HD package to an impressive total of 71 plug-ins with 16 bpc support! If you&#039;re using the bundled CycoreFX standard version that is no less than 10 additional plug-ins in your toolbox. The update also features 9 plug-ins that now also supports 32 bpc (float).

Among other things to mention are a new opacity control for back page in Page Turn, support for "Vertical Cross" in Environment, support for AE lights in Blobbylize, Drizzle, Glass, Glue Gun, Mr. Mercury and Plastic, an improved version of Sphere, new Comp Viewer guide in Power Pin.
